00:00:12.760 --> 00:00:13.760
SHELLY: A WORLD RENOWNED MIXED

00:00:13.760 --> 00:00:14.760
MARTIAL ARTS FIGHTER FACED AN

00:00:14.760 --> 00:00:15.760
ALBUQUERQUE JUDGE TODAY.

00:00:15.760 --> 00:00:16.760
DOUG: JON "BONES" JONES IS

00:00:16.760 --> 00:00:17.730
SUSPECTED RUNNING FROM A CRASH,

00:00:17.730 --> 00:00:18.760
WHERE A PREGNANT WOMAN, SUFFERED

00:00:18.760 --> 00:00:21.800
A BROKEN ARM.

00:00:21.800 --> 00:00:24.150
ACTION 7 NEWS REPORTER AARON

00:00:28.740 --> 00:00:29.740
HILF JOINS US LIVE FROM THE

00:00:29.740 --> 00:00:30.210
COURTHOUSE.

00:00:34.910 --> 00:00:37.350
AARON:

00:00:37.350 --> 00:00:38.080
AU AT EIGHT PRESIDENT ON

00:00:38.080 --> 00:00:38.780
HIS WAY BACK TO LAS VEGAS AFTER

00:00:38.780 --> 00:00:41.190
COMING TO ALBUQUERQUE TO MEET

00:00:41.190 --> 00:00:43.070
WITH JOHN GENOVESE LAYERS.

00:00:46.390 --> 00:00:46.990
HE ENTICED WITH A FELONY AFTER

00:00:46.990 --> 00:00:47.360
LEAVING THE SCENE OF AN

00:00:47.360 --> 00:00:50.360
ACCIDENT.

00:00:50.360 --> 00:00:52.240
UFC LIGHT HEAVYWEIGHT CHAMPION

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:56.340
JOHN JONES --

00:00:56.340 --> 00:00:56.940
JON JONES IN A

00:00:56.940 --> 00:00:58.340
DIFFERENT TYPE OF FIGHT.

00:00:58.340 --> 00:01:03.140
FACING AN ALBUQUERQUE JUDGE

00:01:03.140 --> 00:01:03.880
FACING CHARGES FOR MEN ALLEGE IT

00:01:03.880 --> 00:01:07.250
-- FOR AN ALLEGEDLY HIT AND RUN.

00:01:07.250 --> 00:01:09.250
ALBUQUERQUE POLICE SUSPECTED HE

00:01:09.250 --> 00:01:13.990
RAN A RED LIGHT SUNDAY MORNING.

00:01:13.990 --> 00:01:14.990
HE GOT OUT OF THE CAR AND

00:01:14.990 --> 00:01:15.650
BROKE

00:01:15.650 --> 00:01:20.130
A PREGNANT WOMAN'S ARM.

00:01:20.130 --> 00:01:23.160
AN OPPORTUNITY -- AN OFF-DUTY

00:01:23.160 --> 00:01:23.560
POLICE OFFICER ID HIM AND THEN

00:01:23.560 --> 00:01:28.070
SAW HIM RUN.

00:01:28.070 --> 00:01:28.430
HE TURNED HIMSELF IN MORE THAN A

00:01:28.430 --> 00:01:30.370
DAY LATER.

00:01:30.370 --> 00:01:31.100
IN COURT, HIS ATTORNEY ASKED THE

00:01:31.100 --> 00:01:31.640
JUDGE TO ALLOW HIM TO TRAVEL AS

00:01:31.640 --> 00:01:33.270
PART OF HIS RELIEF.

00:01:33.270 --> 00:01:37.040
-- RELEASE.

00:01:37.040 --> 00:01:39.310
HE IS PART OF A FIGHTER -- HE

00:01:39.310 --> 00:01:43.350
IS A FIGHTER FOR THE UNC.

00:01:43.350 --> 00:01:43.880
AARON: THE JUDGE DID NOT

00:01:43.880 --> 00:01:45.420
RESTRICT HIS TRAVEL.

00:01:45.420 --> 00:01:50.290
THEY ALSO FOUND A PIPE WITH

00:01:50.290 --> 00:01:50.690
MARIJUANA

00:01:50.690 --> 00:01:51.290
, AND AND MMA SPORTS

00:01:51.290 --> 00:01:55.960
MEMORABILIA IN HIS CAR.

00:01:55.960 --> 00:01:58.030
HARLEY -- CLEARLY HE WOULD

00:01:58.030 --> 00:01:59.330
BE

00:01:59.330 --> 00:02:00.400
FOCUSING ON HIS JOB.

00:02:00.400 --> 00:02:01.070
BUT I CAN INITIALLY AS HE IS

00:02:01.070 --> 00:02:04.540
GOING TO DO THE RIGHT THING.

00:02:04.540 --> 00:02:07.570
AARON: AS FOR THE FIGHT ON MAY

00:02:07.570 --> 00:02:08.210
23, THE UFC SAID IT IS REVIEWING

00:02:08.210 --> 00:02:08.670
THE SITUATION AND WILL NOT

00:02:08.670 --> 00:02:13.480
COMMENT EITHER.

00:02:13.480 --> 00:02:14.210
THE DISTRICT ATTORNEY'S OFFICE

00:02:14.210 --> 00:02:17.450
SAYS ONCE THEY HAD RECEIVED THE

00:02:17.450 --> 00:02:18.480
COMPLETED CASE FROM POLICE, THEY

00:02:18.480 --> 00:02:19.220
WILL REVIEW IT AND DECIDE

00:02:19.220 --> 00:02:19.750
WHETHER TO BRING INTO THE GRAND

00:02:19.750 --> 00:02:23.690
JURY FOR INDICTMENT.

00:02:23.690 --> 00:02:26.630
THE PRESIDENT OF THE UFC SAYS

00:02:26.630 --> 00:02:28.590
WHETHER -- SAID HE HAS NOT MADE

00:02:28.590 --> 00:02:29.230
A DECISION ON WHETHER JONES WILL

00:02:29.230 --> 00:02:30.640
FACE DISCIPLINARY ACTION.

